data.description: Nicely updated kitchen with granite slab and manufactured wood flooring.  New carpet on the main. A/C installed last year. Sprinklers in the front with fenced backyard and shed.  Full security system. Only shared wall with the neighbor is the garage. Laundry room upstairs, washer/dryer & refrigerator are included. Seller will consider a credit towards closing costs for loan rate Buydown with strong offer.
